<p>Asks whether JM is interested in publishing A. E. Brehm, <hi rend="italic">Illustrirtes Thierleben</hi> [4 vols. (1864–7)], which has had immense sale on the continent.</p>  
<p>Is making good progress with proofs [of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>].</p> 
